# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# HyGlass website — free integrations. Copy this file to ".env.local" and fill in.
# (.env.local is git-ignored; never commit real keys.)
# After editing, restart the dev server for changes to take effect.
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------

# 1) Enquiry/quote form -> email (Web3Forms, free & unlimited)
#    Sign up at https://web3forms.com with your Gmail, copy the Access Key.
#    Enquiries then arrive in that inbox. Leave blank to keep the "demo" mode
#    (form shows success but sends nothing).
NEXT_PUBLIC_WEB3FORMS_KEY=

# 2) Live chat (Tawk.to, free)
#    Create a free account at https://tawk.to, then:
#    Administration -> Channels -> Chat Widget -> copy the Property ID and Widget ID.
#    Enter them here as "propertyId/widgetId" (e.g. 65abc.../1h9x...).
#    Install the free Tawk mobile app to get notified and reply on the go.
NEXT_PUBLIC_TAWK_ID=
